Game : South Park Rally 
Date : 2003/07/05 
Video: PAL
Ripped by: DCP
Rip notes: nothing was ripped 

The second South Park title on the DC this time puts you in the drivers seat. Choose from the entire cast list and  tear through the streets in you little cart (or trike, or box, whatever you character comes with). Weapons include rockets, Salty Balls, Cheesy Poofs, the beloved Cow and even an Anal probe. All of the voices are also included, making it more like the real cartoon than a rally game.
- Race through South Park Forest, Big Gay Al's Big Gay Animal Sanctuary, or downtown South Park
- Find shortcuts and figure out codes for secret characters 
